label: Mapping
definition: Mapping data model, used for data-mapping between different data models

label: Id
definition: Handle of the Mapping

label: Type
definition: The DOI to the FDO type of the object

label: Status
definition: The status of the Digital Object

label: Version
definition: Version of the Mapping, https://schema.org/version

label: Name
definition: Name of the Mapping as provided by the user, https://schema.org/name
examples: ['Default Mapping for Herbarium of University of Coimbra (COI)']

label: Description
definition: Description of the Mapping as provided by the user, https://schema.org/description
examples: ['The default mapping for the Herbarium of the University of Coimbra (COI) to the Darwin Core standard.']

label: Date Created
definition: Timestamp of creation. Internally generated, https://schema.org/dateCreated

label: Date Modified
definition: Timestamp of last modification. Internally generated, https://schema.org/dateModified

label: Creator
definition: Contains an ods:Agent object

label: Default Mapping
definition: A mapping object setting default values for ods terms. These default mappings will be set for each record in the dataset. Key is the ods term, value the default value to use

label: Field Mapping
definition: Setting an explicit mapping for an ods term to a term from the incoming dataset. Key is the ods term, value the incoming data standard term

label: Mapping Data Standard
definition: Type of data standard we are mapping to

label: Tombstone Metadata
definition: Object containing the tombstone metadata of the object. Only present when ods:status is ods:Tombstone

label: Tombstone Metadata
definition: The tombstone metadata about the tombstoned digital object

label: Tombstoned Date
definition: Timestamp the Digital Object was tombstoned and no longer active.

label: Tombstoned Text
definition: A reason why the Digital Object was tombstoned
examples: ['This is a duplicate of XXX', 'This object was made by mistake']

label: Tombstoned By Agent
definition: The agent who tombstoned the object, contains an ods:Agent object

label: Has Related Pid
definition: The PIDs of the object the tombstoned object is related to

label: Agent
definition: Description of the agents connected to the digital object

label: Name
definition: Full name of the agent

label: Role Name
definition: Indicates the role of the agent, https://schema.org/roleName

label: Start Date
definition: Date the agent began the role

label: End Date
definition: Date the agent ended the role

label: Role Order
definition: Order of the agent in the role. Can be used to indicate the order of importance

label: Email
definition: Email of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Url
definition: URL of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Has Identifier
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Identifier objects
